<body>
<Nav />
<main id="main-content">
  <section class="hero bg-grid" aria-label="Analyzify pricing 2026">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
        <ol style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-4);">
          <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/" style="color:var(--text-4);text-decoration:none;">Home</a></li>
          <li aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--border);">/</li>
          <li style="color:var(--text-3);">Analyzify Pricing 2026</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="hero-dateline">Updated April 2026 · Analyzify pricing analysis · Shopify</div>
      <div style="background:rgba(0,200,100,.06);border-left:3px solid var(--g);padding:14px 20px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin-bottom:24px;max-width:680px;">
        <p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin:0;line-height:1.65;"><strong style="color:var(--g);">Direct answer:</strong> Analyzify costs $99/month (Growth — GA4 + Meta CAPI + Google Enhanced Conversions) or $299/month (Pro — adds TikTok, Snapchat, Pinterest CAPI). No free tier includes server-side tracking.</p>
      </div>
      <h1>Analyzify Pricing 2026 —<br><span class="green">Both Plans</span><br><span class="dim">Broken Down Honestly.</span></h1>
