            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Everything in Growth</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>TikTok Events API (server-side)</li>
