            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Snapchat CAPI</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Priority support + dedicated help</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Advanced customisation</li>
