            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You run ads on <strong style="color:var(--text);">Pinterest or Snapchat</strong> and need server-side coverage there too (Pro plan)</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">Your tracking has been unreliable and you need <strong style="color:var(--text);">expert implementation support</strong> to fix it properly</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You spend <strong style="color:var(--text);">$10,000+/month on Meta Ads</strong> where tracking accuracy has significant revenue impact</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:22px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.03);">
          <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:14px;">✗ ANALYZIFY IS NOT WORTH IT IF...</div>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
