        <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Analyzify charges $99–$299/month primarily to handle the technical setup of tracking configurations that are achievable free with the right tools. The managed service value is real — but most Shopify stores can replicate the GA4 + Meta CAPI + Google Enhanced Conversions + TikTok CAPI outcome using <a href="/capi-shield" style="color:var(--g);">CAPI Shield</a>, the free <a href="/tiktok-events-api-shopify" style="color:var(--g);">TikTok Events API setup</a>, and Shopify's native GA4 channel — at $0. Analyzify Pro at $299/month is most justified for stores running Pinterest or Snapchat Ads at meaningful spend where server-side signals genuinely impact campaign performance.</p>
